| **Bug 1** (claimmail no bag add) | **95%** | Reproduced twice (mail 1 and mail 3). Bag state verified before and after each claim. |
| **Bug 2** (equip no bag deduct) | **95%** | Reproduced with both weapon and armor equips. Bag count unchanged after equip. |
| **Bug 3** (additem auto-equip) | **90%** | Observed with item 3001. May be intentional game design but item loss (displaced 2001) is definitely a bug. |
| **Bug 4** (claimreward wrong message) | **85%** | Reproduced with days 2 and 3 (unclaimed). Day 1 (claimed) shows same message. Clearly a logic error in message selection. |
| **Bug 5** (task progress +1 only) | **90%** | Observed with additem x3 (progress+1) and additem x2 (progress+1). Count is ignored in task trigger. |
| **Bug 6** (collector_100 premature) | **80%** | Achievement name suggests 100 threshold but triggered at 6 items. Could be misnamed achievement or wrong threshold config. |
| **Correlation 1-9** | **95%** | All correlations directly observed in runtime logs during step-through execution. |
